```mermaid
%% 错误处理流程

flowchart TD
    Start[操作开始] --> Validate{数据验证}
    
    Validate -->|失败| ValError[返回 400
    VALIDATION_FAILED]
    ValError --> End1[结束]
    
    Validate -->|通过| Auth{权限检查}
    
    Auth -->|失败| AuthError[返回 403
    ACCESS_DENIED]
    AuthError --> End2[结束]
    
    Auth -->|通过| Storage[存储操作]
    
    Storage -->|成功| Notify[通知前端
    via WebSocket]
    Notify --> Success[返回 200
    + sync_token]
    Success --> End3[结束]
    
    Storage -->|失败| StoreError{错误类型}
    
    StoreError -->|冲突| Conflict[返回 409
    SYNC_CONFLICT]
    Conflict --> ClientResolve[客户端
    选择解决策略]
    ClientResolve --> Storage
    
    StoreError -->|其他| OtherError[返回 500
    STORAGE_FAILED]
    OtherError --> End4[结束]
```
